                                          Main Table
                                      -------------------

  Main Table: - This is the table where we store the all records. if Index filed does not have then go with the main table.

    eg: - querying a record and where condition is on record id or unique id it will tell the salesforce query optimizer 
          go with this particular index in the main table.
